      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "El Kernel construye un contexto de memoria virtual plano,\ncompletamente aislado del resto del sistema operativo.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "El Kernel construye un contexto de memoria virtual plano, completamente aislado del resto del sistema operativo.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "puLsLPfVokFbj9KgFo_r1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2409.5253192070186,
      "y": 1002.1617304307553,
      "width": 281.0078430175781,
      "height": 32.199999999999996,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "hcABl5sE7RZSsDKUTOz-o",
        "Ah76a4Fo7OlMjd7N_UAhR"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 477055372,
      "version": 1737,
      "versionNonce": 480069192,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "fjuePR1GsOaXg4hcTuR0r",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775296837008,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Mapeo de Segmentos",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Mapeo de Segmentos",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "hasTextLink": false,
      "link": null
    },
    {
      "id": "mu6Wflsa59uXAYKHLYpF9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2270.0301404580637,
      "y": 1086.2748247916359,
      "width": 559.998201603915,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Ah76a4Fo7OlMjd7N_UAhR"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 450353972,
      "version": 1659,
      "versionNonce": 26088248,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Identifica los marcados como PT_LOAD y los mapea\ndirectamente desde el disco a las direcciones virtuales\n(p_vaddr) especificadas en la cabecera.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Identifica los marcados como PT_LOAD y los mapea directamente desde el disco a las direcciones virtuales (p_vaddr) especificadas en la cabecera.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "U8CWxAswYL2OefJTmZYmG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2270.0301400843246,
      "y": 1046.844965943151,
      "width": 559.998201603915,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Ah76a4Fo7OlMjd7N_UAhR"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2003880716,
      "version": 1744,
      "versionNonce": 880401480,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "El Kernel itera sobre la Program Header Table del ELF.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "El Kernel itera sobre la Program Header Table del ELF.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QANoeD6jjdpGlLVSQfbhF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2438.0707880403543,
      "y": 1193.6079040974225,
      "width": 223.13189697265625,
      "height": 32.199999999999996,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1BEoEno0eilTS0tRz2A8s",
        "uJ16X7Pa_B2tiSmv192dW"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2MV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 145872524,
      "version": 2021,
      "versionNonce": 418880312,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "_ZBXbcUYzl8WthDVGrAPm",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775296798342,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Dynamic Linking",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Dynamic Linking",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "hasTextLink": false,
      "link": null
    },
    {
      "id": "1OgBpbJwvykby_qrTD78G",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2271.207651942911,
      "y": 1238.9524238118377,
      "width": 558.4281860570887,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "wGxSt1MbUrOplMP9HkxHX",
        "uJ16X7Pa_B2tiSmv192dW"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2018837900,
      "version": 1704,
      "versionNonce": 1351029576,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Si el binario requiere librerías externas (definido por el\nsegmento PT_INTERP), el Kernel no cede el control al\nprograma todavía.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Si el binario requiere librerías externas (definido por el segmento PT_INTERP), el Kernel no cede el control al programa todavía.\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qa6dz4fKcfam0ENmqXljx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2271.60015598905,
      "y": 1326.1647541350706,
      "width": 558.4281860570887,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "lM2-6zdwg3_9HYIoQlcmB",
        "uJ16X7Pa_B2tiSmv192dW"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2NV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1673969716,
      "version": 1967,
      "versionNonce": 765240632,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Pasa el control al enlazador dinámico (ld-linux.so), el cual\nmapea en memoria dependencias críticas como la libc.so.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pasa el control al enlazador dinámico (ld-linux.so), el cual mapea en memoria dependencias críticas como la libc.so.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qJwI7lUlaXMIDnXdevZVT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2417.129332040354,
      "y": 1408.4978330974225,
      "width": 268.9398498535156,
      "height": 32.199999999999996,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CBbQo7AchbWOL8bLVF69E",
        "G6Fc2gmRqtyteIr7Uj1kX"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2108867892,
      "version": 1972,
      "versionNonce": 64318024,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4. Execution Handover",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4. Execution Handover",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "hasTextLink": false,
      "link": null
    },
    {
      "id": "4RAj5HaBW7tOi8XLmjyhY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2271.6001564334965,
      "y": 1452.9213534583025,
      "width": 558.4281860570887,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RMrNCv4drgHuv8POQS6yP",
        "G6Fc2gmRqtyteIr7Uj1kX"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 340272308,
      "version": 2016,
      "versionNonce": 1581465144,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Una vez mapeados los segmentos y resueltas las\ndependencias base, la CPU recibe la instrucción de saltar a la\ndirección definida en el e_entry del ELF Header.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Una vez mapeados los segmentos y resueltas las dependencias base, la CPU recibe la instrucción de saltar a la dirección definida en el e_entry del ELF Header.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iXuBrBZRXyDCaiOCeMeec",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2271.6001558173352,
      "y": 1546.0537925391106,
      "width": 558.4281860570887,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "szogbPqX6wZ1BxiqkRdAP",
        "G6Fc2gmRqtyteIr7Uj1kX"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 727513996,
      "version": 2059,
      "versionNonce": 155246920,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775295864878,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "El programa comienza a ejecutarse.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "El programa comienza a ejecutarse.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
