      "updated": 1775296813192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "SOLUCIÓN",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "dZi3MFyKlYdJEF-H7RImz",
      "originalText": "SOLUCIÓN",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3aSX6hRWM0eQi9says5T0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3513.658292780257,
      "y": 769.163174700097,
      "width": 871.4581769311594,
      "height": 25.014812005855124,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "jv7iCVY-Q2fHmbApFFEjN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1258681144,
      "version": 2416,
      "versionNonce": 55335992,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775296813192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Por motivos de seguridad, Linux implementa ASLR (Address Space Layout Randomization).",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Por motivos de seguridad, Linux implementa ASLR (Address Space Layout Randomization).",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "H8FF7IOCDRaWEcPZp2W6-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3513.658293399353,
      "y": 802.460803403088,
      "width": 871.4581769311594,
      "height": 50.02962401171025,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "jv7iCVY-Q2fHmbApFFEjN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1876415560,
      "version": 2439,
      "versionNonce": 1801495368,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775296813192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Esto significa que la dirección de memoria donde se carga la libc cambia de forma aleatoria cada\nvez que ejecutas el programa.",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Esto significa que la dirección de memoria donde se carga la libc cambia de forma aleatoria cada vez que ejecutas el programa.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qH8-J08xrO36N7YgND0Dv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3513.6582943386547,
      "y": 860.7732441232928,
      "width": 871.4581769311594,
      "height": 25.014812005855124,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "jv7iCVY-Q2fHmbApFFEjN"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5R",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 518175048,
      "version": 2459,
      "versionNonce": 1927550264,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775296813192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Entonces, ¿cómo sabe tu binario a qué dirección exacta de la RAM tiene que saltar?",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Entonces, ¿cómo sabe tu binario a qué dirección exacta de la RAM tiene que saltar?",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hQSab6Q4FR_9OXWE0YWRQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3513.6582950537386,
      "y": 581.5222580843829,
      "width": 871.4581769311594,
      "height": 50.02962401171025,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "C-wXIv_04U2-dJoRSd4jd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5S",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1120951352,
      "version": 2307,
      "versionNonce": 754776648,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775296813192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cuando escribes un programa y usas funciones estándar como printf o malloc, el código de esas\nfunciones no se guarda dentro de tu binario ELF.",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cuando escribes un programa y usas funciones estándar como printf o malloc, el código de esas funciones no se guarda dentro de tu binario ELF.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vVX1-ROAypUFIuwiD_J3q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3513.658292889164,
      "y": 639.7755244884404,
      "width": 898.8043535348216,
      "height": 25.014812005855124,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "C-wXIv_04U2-dJoRSd4jd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5T",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 487113528,
      "version": 2290,
      "versionNonce": 1763487288,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775296813192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Viven en librerías dinámicas externas (como libc.so) que se cargan en la  Memory Mapping Region.",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Viven en librerías dinámicas externas (como libc.so) que se cargan en la  Memory Mapping Region.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MQ4O1jDTAnrgyZJScM8pc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3513.658293175835,
      "y": 1012.7182780157996,
      "width": 871.4581769311594,
      "height": 50.029624011710254,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "c93wmAabUw2zFFkGLfFcE"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5U",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1272670280,
      "version": 2757,
      "versionNonce": 1190555976,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775296813192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Para solucionar esto, Linux no hace llamadas directas, sino que utiliza un sistema de puentes\napoyado en dos estructuras que residen dentro de tu ELF.",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Para solucionar esto, Linux no hace llamadas directas, sino que utiliza un sistema de puentes apoyado en dos estructuras que residen dentro de tu ELF.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
