    {
      "id": "4NUGQZe1St3bwpq1cXGsk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4955.309216820136,
      "y": 772.2407494971039,
      "width": 732.4917602539062,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1332761416,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1322918216,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775296980029,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "En este entorno restringido, el programa está\nciego y aislado.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "En este entorno restringido, el programa está ciego y aislado.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5zNzNJemfUz2Ws64YRlbX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4688.141226669007,
      "y": 662.9385538691762,
      "width": 799.2333169804259,
      "height": 50.029624011710254,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "qQD6Iqg0JnHEY-kfug0x_"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2022253112,
      "version": 3264,
      "versionNonce": 1974091576,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775300350670,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "En Userland, el programa está aislado y sin acceso directo al hardware,\npor sí mismo no puede escribir en pantalla, leer archivos, usar red o gestionar memoria.",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "En Userland, el programa está aislado y sin acceso directo al hardware,\npor sí mismo no puede escribir en pantalla, leer archivos, usar red o gestionar memoria.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "j3E4-qT5idoFU6wZbXXWf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4771.23832104401,
      "y": 744.3548496103939,
      "width": 633.0391281892622,
      "height": 50.029624011710254,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "6Wqpj7IXdmYG69xAcHT6N"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b70",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 621831480,
      "version": 3336,
      "versionNonce": 1166907448,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775300350670,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Para realizar estas acciones, debe solicitar ayuda al Kernel (Ring 0) y\nla única forma de hacerlo es mediante syscalls.",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Para realizar estas acciones, debe solicitar ayuda al Kernel (Ring 0) y la única forma de hacerlo es mediante syscalls.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Pa70zuOFjUtAhOoOz2_bm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5007.355923159579,
      "y": 836.3667439745391,
      "width": 160.80392456054688,
      "height": 32.199999999999996,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "K14Duu7oPkl1LoQSbobza"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b71",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2065648440,
      "version": 1604,
      "versionNonce": 1369297208,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775300350670,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "El mecanismo",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "El mecanismo",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "hasTextLink": false,
      "link": null
    },
    {
      "id": "UMg4l_sKb3-PjU6fFccgp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5104.378938814536,
      "y": 876.7035022952664,
      "width": 797.759765625,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b72",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 655380792,
      "version": 11,
      "versionNonce": 1829174088,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775298113154,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A nivel de código máquina, el Kernel de Linux\nexige que las peticiones se hagan siguiendo unas\nreglas extremadamente estrictas.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A nivel de código máquina, el Kernel de Linux exige que las peticiones se hagan siguiendo unas reglas extremadamente estrictas.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_rGrnVvDAVq4XJnaQr9G5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4771.238321310506,
      "y": 885.9945426215935,
      "width": 633.0391281892622,
      "height": 50.029624011710254,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "IZXu8X0wXNfNtNW5anbNz"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b73",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 66889784,
      "version": 3367,
      "versionNonce": 1094642232,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775300350670,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "En código máquina, el Kernel de Linux impone un contrato muy\nestricto para las peticiones.",
      "fontSize": 20.0118496046841,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "En código máquina, el Kernel de Linux impone un contrato muy estricto para las peticiones.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "F2QD2YB9olHxmvP5QBXGC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4921.605968974542,
      "y": 996.8247652683674,
      "width": 332.3038330078125,
      "height": 32.199999999999996,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
